        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Get in touch</h2>
        <p class="text-white/60 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Ready to get started? Reach out to our team and we'll help you find
          the right CRA service for your needs.
        </p>
